data.description: This is the home you have been waiting for.  Perfectly located in the Woodland Manor Community of Pocomoke.  Close to local schools, restaurants, and shopping.  Includes four bedrooms and two full bathrooms.  Open floorplan kitchen, living room, and dining room.  Lots of high end features...such as granite counter tops, luxury VP flooring, and stainless steel appliances.  Upstairs includes the four bedroom that is great for an office or as an additional room for sleeping.  Large walk in attic space has plenty of room for storage.  Located on a small pond which often gets visited by local wildlife.  Paved driveway and cute little shed on site.  Two car attached garage in addition to the driveway.  Community has sidewalks for your convince.  Located approx. 30 minutes from NASA/Wallops Flight Facility.  Not much further to Chincoteague and Assateague Island, Va.  Also about 30 minutes to other great destinations such as Ocean City to the northeast and Salisbury to the north.  Great location with lots of options close by.  Home was new in 2021 but has been gently lived in.
